Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's problem are ghost hauntings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our cooling hearts are opened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the rumors are solved perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one who sees the truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The child with the brain of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would like to thank these sponsors
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For making this show possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:02:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently ghosts have been haunting Teitan High.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran wanted Kogoro-occhan to solve this mystery,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he refused because he thought that it was nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried about Ran, who's afraid of ghosts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I went along with her to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After school, we started the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the usually empty courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A table and chair suddenly appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My hatred has not dissolved yet..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:35.04,Title,,0,0,0,,The Teitan High Hauntings\N(Part2)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:38.81,Signs,,0,0,0,,Principal's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're asking me if I was standing in the courtyard during the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't go there today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the rain I was in a staff meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One concerning the rumored hauntings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Dr. Araide,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the stretches you taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pain in my hip has lessened immensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did your friends lie to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must've mistaken someone else for the principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go talk to Kazumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}'s friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one resting in the health suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That health suite is very close to the courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So maybe he saw who it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:21.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,Health Suite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,health suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:25.46,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Seko Kunishige.\NTable Tennis Team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After leaving you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been on this bed until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I had left the bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't see the courtyard clearly from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did the principal have to plant those trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So even if anything suspicious happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's the school nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he left early to go driving school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted me to go home and rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since my house is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First the Weeping Storage Room,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the Library of Anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Haunted Staircase,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then the courtyard table and chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is Hosaka thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, we heard that you guys grew up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Together through elementary and middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in high school we rarely met.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as school started, because of a motorcycle accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in the hospital for half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So about him falling off the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found out after I returned to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you seen anyone acting too scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the ones shouting, "Ghost! Ghost!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are behind these hauntings, laughing secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of acting too scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that painter in the art room more suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that person in the health suite is also suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the storage room is close to the health suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the courtyard is right across this hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we have two suspects...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r} is also suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she went to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means she left the library before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, didn't she also suddenly appear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we were investigating the storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she really was behind all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't she have gone home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Dr. Araide and I went to the courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:38.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Art Room\NWhen Dr. Araide and I went to the courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We visited the shoe lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The soil is wet from the front door to the school gate,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no footprints were left there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still in this school!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The four events were all done by the same person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the people who know the most about the incident two years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is most likely to be the culprit of these hauntings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This hallway is always empty after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the teachers all have the staff meeting to attend to,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.26,Signs,,0,0,0,,Health Suite
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first floor health suite,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second floor art room,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the third floor library,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are all places where one could
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secretly, without anyone noticing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move the table and chair from the storage room to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how were the items put there without leaving footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These aren't just pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person behind this must have a motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are some water marks on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They weren't here when we came before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's what I think it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should be marks in the courtyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't wear slippers outdoors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I overlook such an easy trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if this method was used,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them could've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gathering the proof will be hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you gather everyone by the door of the art room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought of a way to catch the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Monobe Masao, Art Student
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,Art Room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long do we have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,VVhat'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we really find the culprit by coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Brat with glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't I tell you not to come in!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you prepared to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prepared to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my things are all over there, so I can leave any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Seiko? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy said that if I came, I'd know who the culprit is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also said that this might take awhile,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tsukamoto Kazumi\NKarate Team
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I gathered my stuff before coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-senpai{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... Why is your umbrella muddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After seeing the morning forecast,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I quickly grabbed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I later found out that I took an old one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't dust your umbrella here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, has the culprit been found yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet. We've just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who is the culprit behind the school hauntings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, didn't you say we'd know if we came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time's school hauntings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are rumored to be caused by Hosaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who died two years age from falling of the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And those stairs are these right by the art room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why don't we all just stay still and wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the spirit of Hosaka to float down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmphl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our purpose for coming
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was to catch the real culprit behind the haungtings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri, forgive me, but I have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving also.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate with you guys being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That brat got us all excited for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you about to begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko is just like my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doing that every time she solves a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the way she fell wasn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me check her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I, Sonoko the Deduction Queen, will begin my deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know the hidden identity behind the ghost hauntings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what, that should be hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see it clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Underwear, underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After solving the mystery, my whole body just relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was actually a simple trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simple trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How the table and chair were placed in the courtyard
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without leaving footprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why note was dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were fooled by that dry note,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgetting one important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the table and chair were moved there during the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The footprints would be washed away by the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if the footprints are washed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The note on the table should've been wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To avoid the rain, Ran, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would find someplace to take cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:11:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe wear a raincoat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the culprit, to prevent the note from getting wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Used something to cover it; an umbrella with strings attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the rain stopped, if you pulled the strings,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The umbrella could be retrieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible to not leave any footprints
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And leave a dry note on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The marks left by the umbrella when it was retrieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, the hall from the courtyard to the classrooms
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has water marks, proving my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were left by the culprit shaking the umbrella off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But merely shaking it doesn't dry it off completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water will still flow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the person behind the ghost hauntings is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the owner of that umbrella with the water flowing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seiko Kunishige!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you pretended to not feel well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you could go to the Health Suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the forecast said that there'd be a sudden rain sometime,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did not know the exact time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you waited until it rained,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then quietly moved the items to the courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Covering them with the umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you returned the Health Suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the rain stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You pulled the strings and retrieved the umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if someone else saw the umbrella on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the first floor, the view is blocked by the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the second or third floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd only think that someone was standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the principal I saw was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw the umbrella and assumed it was the principal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who visited the trees often.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're going to accuse me just because my umbrella's wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My umbrella's wet because it was too dirty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I washed it with faucet water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, using the method that you described,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Monobe and Tsukamoto could've done it also.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suppose we assume that you are culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then all the other hauntings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Including the Library of Anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Cursed Stairwell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the Weeping Storage Room, make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, in the Library of Anger, books that Hosaka once read
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were tossed on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But couldn't anyone do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The borrow logs say who took it out before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you still remember the names of those books?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Names?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One was Electricity Communication...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Electronic Communications Discussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Destruction of Tropical Rain Forests,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,History of the University,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And How Crustal Plates Affect Sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be able to find these books and remember their names,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No person can accomplish that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless that person is his childhood friend who knows him well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about the Cursed Stairwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a puddle beneath the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Seiko also do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, isn't there a hole there where the extinguisher is kept?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After school, Seiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hid a piece of ice in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At night, the ice melted,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the second day, the puddle was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, there's some wax there, so the water didn't gather beside the hole,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no one suspected that the water came from the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one who could do this is Seiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, who lives nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After school, he took the ice from his refrigerator...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you grow up with Hosaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't answer me, I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the Weeping Storage Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To do morning exercises,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A gym student heard weeping in the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was probably Seiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably had table tennis practice that morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And saw Hosaka's belongings for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably thought that Hosaka didn't die of an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I then understood,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Hosaka was murdered when I was in the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I knew what books he read, not because I grew up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because those four books were ones that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka brought when he visited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To help me recover faster,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He read to me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after reading those, he'd think of amazing stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But one day he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that he had gotten a girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upon recovering, I asked around about how he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But all I got was that he had fallen of the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I found the table with his signature on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So to reveal the person who hid his table,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who pushed him off the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I faked the hauntings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka didn't fall because of any pushes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That morning, two sculptures needed to be delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka and I were the hall monitors that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we wanted to secretly move them to the art room,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Place them by the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And surprise the art teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was too hurried and careless,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I accidentally walked past the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka called me, and when I turned around,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My foot slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka, to protect me, was killed beneath the sculpture and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he wasn't pushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.85,0:18:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why was his table in the storage room, gathering dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's so it doesn't disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being the only thing that can prove he was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, his signature was written in ink, it'd soon disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After his accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A notebook with pictures of his classmates was found in his desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we asked the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If on the day we graduated, we could put his table with ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he could graduate with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, the teacher hesitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then we bought a new set to replace it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was placed in the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should've told you earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I found out you guys were close friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the hauntings had already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you appeared at the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought that maybe he'd be by Hosaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So he doesn't have any hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's only angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The plan was all my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day, the first doctor to arrive at the scene was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hung on his mouth were his last words,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If I lie here, won't the teacher be more surprised?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How typical of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Sonoko for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a perfect deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't I remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was shocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Dr. Araide heard that student's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hosaka couldn't have talked in that condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I thought that saying that would comfort the three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it slipped my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Araide is just that kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great to know there're no ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have no problem being monitor next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I should tell my deduction to the newspaper staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And become a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hauntings won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rumors will disappear as time goes by...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I got an important phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye bye, Dr. Araide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. I am Araide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.64,0:22:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To not arouse suspicion and blend into the school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good thing I asked you first
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What that criminal did as me in the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this will be my last conversation with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I have a question to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person that disguised as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Araide sure is helping, like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was she really...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that kind-hearted doctor takes me to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the stretches that you taught me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pain in my hip has lessened immensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Araide is just that kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was she really that evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After talking to school staff and students,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to imagine her as being mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.37,0:23:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be able to smile and kill at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can she be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.18,0:23:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that lady's disguise of you was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even copied your personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.38,0:23:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a frightening type of perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.88,0:24:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.58,0:24:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must've been planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.68,0:24:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.15,0:24:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Crows of the City!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lottery Ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.49,0:24:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the crows of the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.81,0:24:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let the current events staff solve that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your purpose is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trash problem can also be solved on the internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naruhodo
